Stateless Web App: WhatIsTheTime.com

- Allow people to know the time
- We dont need a database
- Start small and can accept downtime
- Want to fully scale vertically and horizontally, no downtime

Concepts which will be explored as part of this solution:

Public IP vs Private IP and EC2 instances
Elastic IP vs Route53 vs Load Balancers
Route 53 TTL, A records and Alias Records
Maintaining Ec2 instances manually vs Auto Scaling Groups
Multi AZ to survive disasters
ELB health checks
Security Group Rules
reservation o capacity for cost saving on Ec2 instance usage when possible

